# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.0.4] - 2024-04-20

### Added

- Stock fetching functionality to the database
- Login and register functionality to the authentication service.
- Route for checking autorization of a request to the authentication service.
- This CHANGELOG file.

### Changed

- Product stock is now managed using StoreProductInstance for easier atomic
  changes.
- Dockerfiles now generate prisma types at build time.
- Schema changes are pushed when container comes online.

### Fixed

- docker compose file was left broken by a rebase.

## [0.0.3] - 2024-04-11

### Added

- Email alerts in the subscription mailing service (by leveraging a cronjob)
- Stores and StoreProduct as database entities

### Changed

- Moved schema.prisma to project root so it can be used by all three services
  without conflicts


## [0.0.2] - 2024-04-04

### Added

- Base functionalities to the subscription mailing service.
- Basic structure to the business service.

## [0.0.1] - 2024-04-04

### Added

- Dockerfiles and docker compose file for the app services.
- Database and database management server to docker compose file.
